# DRMAA Python

### Authors and Contributors
[DRMAA Python](https://github.com/pygridtools/drmaa-python) was originally written by [Enrico Sirola](https://github.com/esirola).

It was ported to Python 3 and is currently maintained by [Dan Blanchard](https://github.com/dan-blanchard/).

### Documentation
For the most up-to-date documentation, use [our RTD page](http://drmaa-python.readthedocs.org/). 

We also have an [older publicly modifiable wiki](https://github.com/pygridtools/drmaa-python/wiki).
